data.description: Immaculate renovated home located in Cul-de-sac minutes from I -85 AND GA 316. This Great Property is located convenient to Restaurant's, shopping, Top Golf and Much more. The home features 4 Large Bedrooms and 3 Full Baths. A Large family/great room with a Vaulted Ceiling. All new Floors Hardwood and Tile floors. New Paint, Light Fixtures throughout. Kitchen has All New Stainless Steel appliances included (Dishwasher, French Drawer Refrigerator, Range, Microwave) and Granite Counter tops and subway tile. The lower level includes spacious bedroom with walk in closet plus private bathroom/This room also features a potential family room use as well. Room is wired with a State of the art home theater speaker system that plays throughout the house *Master Bedroom has a huge walk-in closet & private suite inside *Master Bath has double granite sinks, separate shower and Soaker tub *Hallway bath is also renovated with new vanity and granite countertops. Two additional cozy bedrooms in addition to the master on the upper level *Very large Backyard with new deck.
